{"tid":613004,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"雲南米線 vs 桂林米粉","createTime":"2018-04-01T09:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T13:19:04.000Z","uid":54832,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e79cb735f092366cd4ce6b3fe24c0ca101b6432c","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"兩者分別 我覺得桂林米粉係比米線粗少少同滑身d<br />\n<br />\n老母鄉下係廣州 有印象細個探親時食親都係桂林米粉配牛腩牛肉酸菜多<br />\n<br />\n果時雲南米線根本沒咩市場，點解香港而家會變成咁 因為大陸人多左所以食米線？定係香港人口味同大陸同化<br />\n<br />\n譚仔本身只係一間賣平既垃圾麵店 而家仲愈來愈貴<br />\n其他細舖又跟佢加價<br />\n<br />\n最近係細舖食到碗桂林牛腩米粉都係26$ <br />\n講咁多廢話其實想問下大家有沒好食既桂林米粉推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edc6fc7a220971a74cba7ecbe1f8d535a0789b6","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/180028_954c0af7ffbe356bad808b3dac8d4d34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F180028_954c0af7ffbe356bad808b3dac8d4d34.png&h=4c2e9383&s={SIZE}\" />桂林米粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/180030_cb7b4b889e79f6bafb317822dcac2b90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F180030_cb7b4b889e79f6bafb317822dcac2b90.png&h=dbbea15b&s={SIZE}\" />雲南米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5582b0e0eeb3e4b19caab9e8b6aa9a91dcd36b","tid":613004,"uid":2360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"桂林米粉係易夾版嘅瀨粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b9c935306728a2ba561532a44a8986cf9cdfdf","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc5582b0e0eeb3e4b19caab9e8b6aa9a91dcd36b","tid":613004,"uid":2360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"桂林米粉係易夾版嘅瀨粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:14:47.000Z","msg":"感覺上瀨粉好似好難消化咁"},{"pid":"515df6585b8899d4dfa68e5805240ba2733fbbb5","tid":613004,"uid":71257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"譚仔都唔係正宗雲南米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係麵底限死係米線/薯粉嘅車仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888f701d8e99d61db523b7ce5924dbc9b3f8d84e","tid":613004,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"其實雲南米線係好食<br />\n不過唔係譚仔果種"},{"pid":"9806f876f82040f38e53136e39a41aa5278ef1a5","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"太多人自稱係正宗雲南米線<br />\n但係全部都係面底再加餸既酸辣粉"},{"pid":"c939e2dc2392c456b2024c4ac40e3cef0c425b95","tid":613004,"uid":52599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"桂林米粉可以試下元朗陸記，雖然應該唔係正宗，但幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1906c0ddfe4cec95c483824d1933644f7fd97b0e","tid":613004,"uid":16272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"事實上桂林米粉係香港真係好炒食到好食/正宗"},{"pid":"167f30e8a9ce4128c45885b84e22022277331de1","tid":613004,"uid":95838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c939e2dc2392c456b2024c4ac40e3cef0c425b95","tid":613004,"uid":52599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"桂林米粉可以試下元朗陸記，雖然應該唔係正宗，但幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"ae0003bce6beb5dc43344238b3bfd0158ec36b49","tid":613004,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"譚仔本身就唔垃圾，係連鎖之後差左啫"},{"pid":"1fe7ae757941b2e432628feaadcf6bd2d7f31f7e","tid":613004,"uid":30100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"正宗桂林米粉要有一定既配料<br />\n包括花生、叉燒絲、牛肚絲，酸豆角<br />\n同埋其實所謂既過橋米粉<br />\n係應該一鍋滾雞湯<br />\n係食客面前落米粉同餸<br />\n而大陸既米線同米粉 同香港係完全相反"},{"pid":"a97c768411718cf22e46131efc7da8af7d2e4d9e","tid":613004,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0003bce6beb5dc43344238b3bfd0158ec36b49","tid":613004,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"譚仔本身就唔垃圾，係連鎖之後差左啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"轉手之後仲垃圾<br />\n<br />\n樓下間垃圾譚仔 冇一日會坐滿"},{"pid":"9a2b9a2d35a61568968ece36695977b218dc163e","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c939e2dc2392c456b2024c4ac40e3cef0c425b95","tid":613004,"uid":52599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"桂林米粉可以試下元朗陸記，雖然應該唔係正宗，但幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"本身係元朗牛屎佬 學生時代食過 佢太雜 金學生餐 連飯都有 真係唔太正宗"},{"pid":"d0bf65cc16eca4e87d67ce7d2bae707404cff6ad","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n真係沒人食開桂林米粉 ?<br />\n個個食譚仔"},{"pid":"8ab3c14d5c0ce4926af5a301d2f22a265b03f8ad","tid":613004,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe7ae757941b2e432628feaadcf6bd2d7f31f7e","tid":613004,"uid":30100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"正宗桂林米粉要有一定既配料<br />\n包括花生、叉燒絲、牛肚絲，酸豆角<br />\n同埋其實所謂既過橋米粉<br />\n係應該一鍋滾雞湯<br />\n係食客面前落米粉同餸<br />\n而大陸既米線同米粉 同香港係完全相反"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T17:41:13.000Z","msg":"師兄有沒係香港食過間唔錯？"},{"pid":"6ef96a11cda1f539aa476e4e8f855a26fb3749af","tid":613004,"uid":151925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"